==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Roche alum
<hw>Roche" al`um</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A kind of
alum occuring in small fragments; -- so called from <xex>Rocca</xex>, in
Syria, whence alum is said to have been obtained; -- also called
<altname>rock alum</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rochelime</ent>⟦br⟧
